                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6950" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1738</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8401 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝沃“复兴”踩雷：福田汽车多元化折戟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Borgward&#39;s revival stepped on a landmine: the failure of Foton Motor Company&#39;s diversification</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄怡，祝天雅，马昕宇，侯媛敏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北汽福田汽车股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福田汽车；宝沃汽车；多元化并购；战略转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Foton Motor Company; Borgward Motor Company; Diversified M&amp;A; Strategic Transition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汽车行业因综合度高、产业链长的特点，一直以来都是国民经济的重要支柱，具有巨大的市场需求空间。而其中最重要的两个细分市场——乘用车及商用车市场由于使用用途及客户群体的差异，又具有截然不同的市场体量。本案例系统讲述了商用车龙头企业福田汽车在行业下行的压力下，意图通过并购乘用车品牌宝沃汽车实现“商乘并举”的多元化转型，却因种种原因导致经营不善，无奈转手后，又因剥离方式不当再度生变，遭受巨额损失的全过程，旨在引导学员思考福田汽车在多元化并购及资产剥离过程中存在的问题，总结福田汽车多元化战略最终折戟的原因，同时为同类企业从事多元化并购活动提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The automobile industry has been an important pillar of the national economy due to its high comprehensiveness and long industrial chain, with a huge space of market requirements. However, the two most important market segments - Passenger Car and Commercial Vehicle - have distinct market demand due to the differences in usage and customer groups between them. This case completely describes the whole process of Foton Motor Company, a leading enterprise of Commercial Vehicles, tried to realize the diversification transformation of &quot;developing both Passenger Car and Commercial Vehicle&quot; by acquiring Borgward, a brand of Passenger Car, to cope with the pressure from industry struggling. However, Borgward was forced to divest because of mismanagement, and the new changes which was caused by improper divestiture have led to huge losses again. The purpose is to guide the students to think about the problems in diversification M&amp;A and divestiture activities of Foton Motor Company, summarize the reasons for the failure of its strategy. In addition, it provides a reference for similar enterprises to engage in diversified M&amp;A activities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购类型；并购动因；多元化并购的风险；多元化与核心竞争力；资产剥离的类型；多元化战略对企业能力的要求</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
